title: Google Analytics 101: Maximizing Your Website Traffic's Potential
description: Elevate your law firm's SEO game by enhancing your Google Analytics (GA4) knowledge in our upcoming webinar. Discover how to utilize key features like data tracking for your website’s traffic, page performance, and more to understand your website’s online presence holistically as we walk you through the interface top to bottom. Whether you're a seasoned attorney or just starting out, this session will give you a better understanding of Google Analytics and how you can use it to assess your site’s health and performance.
